title: Rainbow
content:
Rainbow may refer to:

  • Rain bow, a cosmetic variant of the short bow
  • Afro, rainbow-coloured clue scroll reward
  • Fancy boots, rainbow-coloured boots from the Stronghold of Security
  • Beanie, primary-colored beanie as easy clue scroll reward
  • Propeller hat, obtained through the Easter Event
  • Clown trousers, rainbow-colored trousers from the Halloween holiday event
  • Rainbow partyhat, obtained through the Christmas Event
  • Rainbow fish
  • Rainbow scarf, and the strands it consists of:
    • Red rainbow strand
    • Orange rainbow strand
    • Yellow rainbow strand
    • Green rainbow strand
    • Blue rainbow strand
    • Purple rainbow strand


 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
